# WildLife: The Card Game - Image Asset Documentation

This directory contains the graphical assets for the game, organized as sprite sheets (atlases) to optimize performance and memory.

## Sprite Sheets (Atlases)

| File | Category | Usage |
| :--- | :--- | :--- |
| `small.png` | Life Cards | Small Animals (Fox, Squirrel, Raccoon). |
| `big.png` | Life Cards | Big Animals (Bear, Elk, Deer, Boar). |
| `flying.png` | Life Cards | Flying Animals (Owl, Eagle, Robin). |
| `aquatic.png` | Life Cards | Aquatic Animals (Koi, Axolotl, Salmon). |
| `enhancers.png` | Enhancers | Multipliers for all life categories. |
| `threats.png` | Aggressors | Predators, Hunters, and Catastrophes (Fire/Pollution). |
| `special.png` | Utilities | Rain, Protectors, and First Player Token (CSS). |

## Implementation Notes

- **PHP Logic**: Definitions for sprite indices are managed in `modules/php/Managers/CardManager.php`.
- **CSS Styling**: The first player token background is handled in `wildlife.css` under the `.wld_first-player-token` class.
- **JS Rendering**: Sprite URLs and coordinate calculations are performed in `Game.js` within the `createCardElement` method.
